Package gui

This package consits of all the different GUI windows that the game contains
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FinalScreen
    The screen that appears when the game is finished or won.
    GuiManager
    The class that manages all the GUI classes.
    MainScreen
    The first screen of the game.
    NewWorld
    The space outpost screen of the game.
    setupscreen
    The screen which enables the player to select the crew members and name the ship.
    ShipStock
    The screen that displays the Food and medicine inventory to the player.
    ThirdScreen
    The main screen of the game that contains all the crew member details, ship details and the action buttons.
